race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi F&M Handciap
race.comment: EMPIRE OF PAIN (5) is worth another try in what looks a suitable race for her. Back in class after finishing last of four last time and winning rider goes back aboard. Best figures stack up and can atone. TREMAMORE (3) was a determined winner fresh then hit the line hard latest when fifth over 1400m at Warrnambool. Can find winning form again. POLISH PLAYGIRL (10) ran a much improved race second-up to score her maiden success. Tricky gate here but Shinn stays aboard and should be hard to hold out again. MISS CASTELVECCHIO (8) returns from a break and looks well placed here. Did win when last resuming and draws for a soft run with cover throughout in this. Will just need the break in the straight. DIVINE TURF (7) just missed last time when second run back and is a third-up winner. Drawn well and should be ready to fire.
